时最高气温预报，到 5 月 16 日前后，不仅河北天津山东三省市成为我国北方地区烧烤型高温天气的重点区域，而且部分地区最高气温可能达到 40 度以上。这是今年以来北方地区最强的一次高温过程，一般来说，北方的干热高温季节出现在雨季开始前的 6 月，5 月中旬就出现这样的炎热是较为罕见的。烧烤型高温或大范围出现，局部有 40 度可能性！超算：山东河北中心"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d35ce0c535f39b7b4c8259256bdc7a86_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "13 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/600517301"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IruT60Izc0c0tEAMaCDk1NzI4ODIwII2V9qIGMAE4bEApcgk2MDA1MTczMDF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1683942897.294775", "card_id": "Q_600395673", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 89}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "年轻人不爱社交、出现「卡顿」，更多的是心理逃避还是单纯觉得没必要？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-88cfc90611a00c4777f29a93fb6885e2_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "13 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/600395673"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IruT60Izc0c0tEAMaCDk1NzAxNjk1IObs8qIGMAI43QFAKnIJNjAwMzk1NjczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1683942897.2955568", "card_id": "Q_599661839", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 56}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "当我们无故失眠时，我们的身体在发生什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-09dc2b2c53688a5564e772f3e73ffc29_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "13 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/599661839"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IruT60Izc0c0tEAMaCDk1NTM4NzY5IPun4KIGMAI4uwFA